Name: ampulla of Vater adenocarcinoma
Definition: An ampulla of Vater carcinoma that derives_from epithelial cells of glandular origin.

Name: ampulla of Vater squamous cell carcinoma
Definition: An ampulla of Vater carcinoma that derives_from epithelial squamous cells.
Synonym: squamous cell carcinoma of middle ear

Name: ampulla of Vater small cell carcinoma
Definition: A hematologic cancer that is located in the blood or bone marrow that doesn't respond to treatment.
